commit message:
Merge pull request #212 from win32re/patch-1

Update strings.xml

Updated gradle android plugin to 1.1.2.
Removed support-annotations.
Fixed minor compilation issue with new jlibtorrent.
No more vuze code in android.
Fixes false positive toast on files that couldn't be shared
Fixes NPE on Photo Selection Dialog.
Fixes bug where file descriptors fetched by content:// uris wouldn't have a disk path available

Merge pull request #197 from cheako/issue-72.0

Be descriptive about why NullPointerException.
Fixes playlist refresh issues when removing from playlist or deleting files.
Fixed a merge related compilation issue.
Added new strings and corrected a few old ones
Remove extra return in pl strings.xml.
avoids crash on IllegalStateException when saving player queue
New Tipping menu actions for compatible torrent transfers. #bitcoin & #fiat
Removed label parameter. message= didn't work either on Circle, nor Mycelium.
package name refactor, post frostwire-common adjustments

Updating Chinese translation

This translation was made by a translator via Elance
Removed remaining unused code related to in app billing.

Merge pull request #218 from muckachina/master

Updating Chinese translation
Removed duplicated entries from zh strings.
Remove 'Play All' menu item if play list is empty
Fixes Wi-Fi sharing issue from Audio Player screen. Social Sharing message refers to #FrostWire
Avoids notifying more than once for a finished torrent download. Needs more testing.
use the notifiedDat file as the synchronization lock
move away from appending sha1 byte arrays, into serializing a bloom filter
Integrated Java Bloom Filter to keep track of previous notifications while maintaining user's download history privacy
rename wrongly named upnp preference to enable_wifi_sharing

No more support for old armeabi architecture. See https://github.com/mono/MonoGame/wiki/Properly-supporting-Android-ARM-devices and http://android.stackexchange.com/questions/34958/what-are-the-minimum-hardware-specifications-for-android
Adding icons for Bitcoin/Fiat Tipping actions.
Show donation icons on transfer list when donation options are available.
fixes bug where the last favorite song removed would not be cleared.
similar issue with 'Last added' playlist fixed.
New IS_GOOGLE_PLAY_DISTRIBUTION. Cleanup: amazon distro, tv menu item, free apps menu item, appia.
